OL,3,C'I'm ready now': Celine Dion shares
OL,4,Cemotional health update in new trailer
OL,6,FCeline Dion has shared details of her
OL,7,Fhealth struggles with Stiff Person
OL,8,FSyndrome, in a new trailer for her
OL,9,Fupcoming documentary.
OL,11,FThe Canadian singer announced she had
OL,12,Fbeen diagnosed with , which causes
OL,13,Fmuscle stiffening and spasming, in
OL,14,F2022.
OL,16,F"I wasn't ready to say anything
OL,17,Fbefore," Dion says of her illness in
OL,18,Fthe trailer, "but I'm ready now."
