OL,6,FThe new documentary, called I Am:
OL,7,FCeline Dion, will offer a behind-the-
OL,8,Fscenes look at how Dion copes with her
OL,9,Fillness, and the lengths she has gone
OL,10,Fto
OL,12,FThe 56-year-old was forced to cancel
OL,13,Fher Las Vegas residency in 2021, as
OL,14,Fwell as
OL,16,F"I'm working so hard every day," the
OL,17,Fsinger says tearfully in the trailer,
OL,18,F"It's not hard to do a show. It's hard
OL,19,Fto cancel a show."
