OL,4,Cemotional health update in new trailer
OL,6,F"I miss it so much. The people, I miss
OL,7,Fthem," she continues, but says she is
OL,8,Fdetermined to perform again: "If I
OL,9,Fcan't run, I'll walk. If I can't walk,
OL,10,FI'll crawl. I won't stop."
OL,12,FFans responded to the trailer, with
OL,13,Fone commenting on YouTube: "This is
OL,14,Fjust the trailer, but I'm already
OL,15,Fcrying like a baby."
OL,17,F"I started to cry from the first
OL,18,Fsecond of this video," wrote another,
OL,19,F"what a powerful woman."
