OL,3,C'I'm ready now': Celine Dion shares
OL,4,Cemotional health update in new trailer
OL,6,FAs snippets of Dion's music play in
OL,7,Fthe trailer, she says: "My voice is
OL,8,Fthe conductor of my life. When your
OL,9,Fvoice brings you joy, you're the best
OL,10,Fof yourself. I need my instrument."
OL,12,FFurther clips show the My Heart Will
OL,13,FGo On singer doing physiotherapy,
OL,14,Finterspersed with clips of her old
OL,15,Fconcerts.
OL,17,FIn December, Dion's sister Claudette
OL,18,Fsaid the singer was no longer in
OL,19,Fcontrol of her muscles.
