OL,3,C'I'm ready now': Celine Dion shares
OL,4,Cemotional health update in new trailer
OL,6,FIn January, Dion said that although
OL,7,Fthe condition was a "challenge", she
OL,8,Fwas "learning how to live with and
OL,9,Fmanage it, but not let it define me."
OL,11,FShe added that she was making the
OL,12,Fdocumentary to "try to raise awareness
OL,13,Fof this little-known condition, to
OL,14,Fhelp others who share this diagnosis."
OL,16,FThe documentary will be released on
OL,17,FPrime Video on June 25.
